        "Chain reorganizations: indexers wait for N confirmations and roll back then replay affected blocks so the UI never shows an orphaned trade as final.",
        "RPC provider outage: apps configure multiple providers (e.g., Alchemy with an Infura fallback) with automatic failover and retry-with-backoff.",
